{"tid":1179160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google宣布禁止販售大麻及相關製品的APP","createTime":"2019-05-31T02:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T07:15:51.000Z","uid":28765,"like":12,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a5e17699ec9c0a386ae0eb0db56766164a3f6e","tid":1179160,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:18:03.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕網路科技巨擘Google公司宣布，將禁止Play商店中存在販賣大麻及相關製品的APP，以符合該公司新的內容政策。<br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導，Google公司30日宣布，為配合該公司修訂的內容政策，將禁止Play商店中任何提供大麻與相關製品販售服務的APP，現存的APP必須在30天期限內改善。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle發言人向《路透》表示，開發者只需要將「購物車」的功能移出APP，就會符合Google的新規定。官方正與許多開發者合作，以提供技術支援，好讓他們在不打擾顧客的情況下對APP作出更動。<br />\n<br />\n對此，美國大麻快遞APP公司「Eaze」發言人則表示：「Google作出了令人遺憾的決定，這項改變只會助長非法市場的交易。但我們相信Google、Apple和Facebook最終一定會選擇正確的做法。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2807603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2807603&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=3b4a0873\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2807603&h=bc0ee5e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2807603</a>"},{"pid":"a62fbdda4dd4a67ad0f48ef97cf6770111c5883e","tid":1179160,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:35:30.000Z","msg":"香港應該唔會顯示到呢類應用程式(因為本身違法) <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac06135d8cfd98ac0e2fa6d291899a957d85cd9","tid":1179160,"uid":22675,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ox6hWUC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOx6hWUC.png&h=0ae5e8b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6799ecd1c6ff9df9cf52c97881d2aabe0cb5f78","tid":1179160,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T12:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a